hadiths[139]{hadithnumber,text}:
4020,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi naya kapda hasil kartey to uska naam letey yani qamis ya pagdi waghaira aur ye dua padhtey : (اللهم لك الحمد أنت كسوتنيه أسألك من خيره وخير ما صنع له وأعوذ بك من شره وشر ما صنع له) ''aey Allah ! teri hi tareef hai, to ne mujhey ye pehnaya hai, main tujh se uski khair aur bhalai ka sawal karta hun aur us bhalai ka jis ke liye isey banaya gaya hai, main iskey shar se teri panah chahta hun aur us shar se jis ke liye isey banaya gaya hai. Abu-Nazara ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se jab koi naya kapda pahntaa to usey yun dua di jaati (تبلي ويخلف الله تعالى) ''Allah karey tum isey khoob (istimal karkey) puraanaa karo aur Allah iskey baad aur bhi inayat farmaai ."
4021,"Musaddad ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha hamen Esa bin Yunus ne bayan kiya ba-waasta Jareeri ke, unhoney apni sanad se mazkura baala ki manind riwayat kiya."
4022,"Muslim bin Ibrahim ne bayan kiya, unhoney kaha hamein Muhammad bin Dinar ne bayan kiya ba-waasta Jareeri ke, unhoney apni sanad se mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Abdul-Wahaab Saqafi ne apni sanad mein Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahin kya. aur Hammad bin Salma ne kaha : (عن الجريري an أبي العلاء an النبي ﷺ). Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Hammad bin Salma aur (Abdul-Wahaab) Saqafi dono ka samaa, (suna) eik jaisa hai. (dono mursal bayan kartey hain.)"
4023,Janab Sehal apney walid Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs khana khaney ke baad yun dua karey : (الحمد لله الذي أطعمني هذا الطعام ورزقنيه من غير حول مني ولا قوة) ''hamd us Allah ki jisney mujhey ye khana khilaya aur baghair meri kisi koshish aur quwwat ke mujhey ye rizq inayat farmaya.'' to uskey agley aur pichhley sab gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain. farmaya : aur jo koi kapda pehney phir ye dua karey : (الحمد لله الذي كساني هذا الثوب ورزقنيه من غير حول مني ولا قوة) ''hamd us Allah ki jisney mujhey ye kapda pehnaya aur baghair meri kisi koshish aur quwwat ke mujhey ye inayat farmaya.''  to uskey agley aur pichhley (sab) gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain.
4024,"Hazrat Umme-Khalid binte Khalid bin Saeed bin Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuchh kapdey laye gaey, un main eik chhoti si dhaari daar ooni chadar bhi thi. aapney farmaya : ''tumhara kya khayal hai ke uska ziyada haq daar kon hai?''  to Sahaba khamosh rahey. phir aapney farmaya : ''Umme-Khalid ko merey paas lao.'' usey laya gaya to ye aapney usey odhaa di. phir farmaya :(أبلي وأخلقي) ''Allah karey tum isey khoob pahno aur puraanaa karo.'' aapney ye do baar farmaya. aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) is chadar ki surkh ya zard dhaariyaan dekhney lagey aur farmatey jatey they : (سناه سناه ya أم خالد) aur ye lafz Habshi zaban mein ''khoobsurat'' ke maani mein aata hai. (yani bahut khoobsurat , bahut khoobsurat hai aey Umme- Khalid !)."
4025,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tamam kapdon mein se qamis ziyada pasand thi.
4026,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko qamis se badh kar aur koi kapda ziyada pasand nahin tha.
4027,Hazrat Asma binte Yazid bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qamis ki aasteen (aap ke) pahunchey (gattey) tak hua karti thi.
4028,Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qubaaen (chadar) taqseem kin magar Makhrima ko kuchh na diya. to Makhrima ne kaha : aey bete ! chalo ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein chaltey hain. to main unke sath chal pada . phir unhoney mujh se kaha : andar jao aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bula laao. chunanche maine aap ko bulaya to aap tashrif ley aaye aur aap unhi qubaaon (chadaron) mein se eik odhey huey they. aapney farmaya : ''ye maine tumharey liye chhupa rakhi thi.'' isliye Makhrima ne usey dekha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya Makhrima razi hai?'' Quteba ne sanad mein ''ibne-Abi Mulaika'' kaha aur uska naam nahin liya.
4029,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marfooan riwayat hai (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne) farmaya : ''jisney shohrat wala libas pehna Shan Wala Allah qiyamat ke din usey usi jaisa libas pahnaaeyga.'' Abu-Awaana se mazeed riwayat hua hai : ''phir uskey liye is mein aag bhadke gi.''
4030,Musaddad ne Abu-Awaana se riwayat kiya ke (Allah usey qiyamat ke roz) ''zillat ka libas pahnaaey ga.''
4031,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney kisi qom se mushaabihat ikhtiyar ki to wo unhi mein se hua.''
4032,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahir tashrif laye jabkey aap baalon ki bani hui kajawon jaisey naqsh wali siyah rang ki chadar odhey huey they. aur Husain ne sanad yun bayan ki (حدثنا يحيى بن زكريا) yani ibne-Abi Zaayda ki bajaey asal naam aur nasab zikr kiya.  Hazrat Utba bin Abd Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se libas manga to aapney mujhey kataan (bareek aur qeemti) ke do kapdey inayat farmaey. phir maine apney aap ko dekha to main apney sathiyon mein umda libas wala tha."
4033,Janab Abu-Barda se riwayat hai ke merey walid ne mujh se kaha : aey bete ! agar tum hamein dekhtey jabke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath hotey they aur ham par barish ho jati to tum samajhtey ke ham se bhedon ki si boo aati hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maqsad hai ke oon ke libas ki wajeh se.
4034,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Shaah Zi Yoozan  (banu Hameer) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik hulla (kapdon ka joda) hadiya bheja jo usney tentis oonton ya oontniyon ke badley mein kharida tha. isliye aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey qubul farma liya.
4035,Is-haq bin Abdullah bin Haris ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bees se kuch ooper oontniyaan de-kar eik joda kharida aur phir Zi Yoozan ki taraf hadiya bhej diya.
4036,Hazrat Abu-Barda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan hazir hua to unhoney hamein eik mota tehband dikhaya jaisey ke Yamen mein bantey hain aur eik ooni chadar jisey (malbada) kehtey hain (ba-wajah pewand lagey honey ke ya mota honey ke usey malbada kaha gaya hai) unhoney Allah ki qasam uthai aur kaha : bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat un do kapdon mein hui thi.
4037,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke jab harooriya (khaarijiyon) ka zuhoor hua aur main Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aaya, to unhoney (mujh sey) kaha ke main un logon ke paas jaun. to maine eik khoobsurat yamni hulla zebe-tan kiya (pehna). Abu-Zameel ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Abbas badey khoob-roo aur wajeeha jawan they. ibne-Abbas ne bataya ke main un logon ke paas pahuncha to unhoney mujhey marhabaa kaha : aur boley aey ibne-Abbas ! ye hulla kaisa hai? (yani aapney usey kyonkar zeb tan kya hai?) to unhoney jawab diya ke tum mujh par kya aetiraz kartey ho, halanke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko intehai khoobsurat hulla zebe tan kiye (pehne) dekha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Abu-Zameel ka naam Simaak bin Waleed Hanfi hai."
4038,"Janab Abdullah bin Saad apney walid Saad (Raazi Ashtaki) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Bukhaara main eik shakhs ko dekha jo apney safed khachchar par Sawar tha aur uskey sar par siyah ki pagdi thi. usney kaha : ye mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pahnaai thi. ye lafz Usman (bin Muhammad Inmaati) ke hain aur uski riwayat mein (''أخبرنا'') ke lafz hain."
4039,"Abdur-Rehman bin Ghanam Ash'ari ne kaha ke mujhey Janab Abu-Aamir ya Abu-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya aur Allah ki qasam , qasam dusri baar , unhoney mujh se jhoot nahin kaha, unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''yaqeenan meri ummat mein aisey log aaeyngey jo khaz aur resham ko halal samjhen gey.'' phir kuchh bayan kiya. iskey baad farmaya : ''kaee un mein se qiyamat tak ke liye bandar bana diye jaeyngey aur kaee khinzir. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se bees ya ziyada ke mutalliq marwi (bayan) hai ke wo khaz pehantey they. un mein Hazrat Anas bin Malik aur Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka naam bhi hai."
4040,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke masjid ke darwazey ke paas eik dhaari daar reshmi hulla farokht kiya ja raha tha. to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! agar aap usey kharid lein aur Jume ke din aur waadon ke istaqbal ke moqe par jab wo aap ke paas aatey hain, zeb tan farmaya (pehna) keren (to bahut khoob rahey.) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to wo log pehantey hain jinka aakhirat mein koi hissey nahin.'' baad iske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas usi qism ke hulley aagey to aapney Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi un mein se eik hulla inayat farmaya. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap mujhey ye ata farma rahey hain, halanke aapney utaarid waley hulley ke baarey mein aisey aisey farmaya tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine ye tumhen tumharey apney pehanney ke liye nahin diya hai.'' chunanche Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apney mushrik bhai ko jo makkey mein tha, dey diya."
4041,Janab Salim apney walid Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se ye qissa bayan kartey hain. unhoney ((حلة سيراء) ki bajaey) (حلة إستبرق) kaha. (istabraq motey resham ko kehtey hain.) is riwayat mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko deebaaj (bareek resham) ka eik hulla bhijwaayaa aur farmaya : ''usey farokht karkey apni zarurat puri kar lo.''
4042,"Abu-Usman Nahdee se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Utba bin Farqad ko likha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne resham se mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke is-is qadr ho yani do , teen , chaar ungli ke barabar."
4043,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dhaari daar hulla hadiya diya gaya , jo aapney mujhey bhijwa diya. mein usey pehan kar aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine aap ke chehrey par ghussay ke aasaar dekhay . phir aapney farmaya : ''maine ye tumhen isliye nahin bheja ke tum khud isey pehan lo.'' chunanche aapney mujhey hukm diya to maine usey apney khandan ki aurton mein taqseem kar diya."
4044,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya hai ke Qassi pehna jaey. (wo reshmi kapda jo Misr se daraamad hota tha) ya za'fraani zard rang ke kapdey pehney jaeyn ya soney ki anguthi pahni jaey ya rukoo ki haalat mein Quran ki qirat ki jaey.
4045,Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha ke aapney rukoo aur sajdey mein qirate-Quran se mana farmaya hai.
4046,Ibrahim bin Abdullah ne ye riwayat bayan ki) Hazrat Ali ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey mana farmaya hai) is mein ye mazeed bayan kiya : main ye nahin kehta ke tum logon ko mana kiya hai.
4047,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Shaahe-Rome ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bareek resham ka eik chogha hadiya bheja . aapney usey pehna . main goya uski lahraati aastinon ko dekh raha hun. phir aapney usey Hazrat Jaafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan bhej diya. unhoney usey pehna aur aap ki khidmat mein aaye . to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine ye tumhen tumharey pehanney ke liye nahin diya hai.'' unhoney kaha : to phir main iska kya karun ? aapney farmaya : ''isey apney bhai Najashi ke paas bhej do.'' (yani Shaahe-Habsha ke yahan bhej do.)
4048,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main surkh rang ki argwaani zeen posh par Sawar nahin hota, na zard rang ka libas pahntaa hun aur na aisi qamis pahntaa hun jiski aasteenein resham se kaadhi gaee hon.'' Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) ne riwayat bayan karney ke dauran main apni qamis ke daman ki taraf ishara kiya aur mazeed kaha : ''khabrdar ! mardon ki khushbu (zeenat) mein mahak hoti hai rang nahin hota aur khabrdar ! aurton ki khushbu (zeenat) mein rang hota hai mahak nahin hoti. Saeed bin Abi Aruba ne kaha : muhaddeseen kiram aurton ki khushbu ke mutalliq mazkura farman ko is maani mein letey hain ke jab wo ghar se bahir niklen to aisi khushbu na lagaeyn jo mahak wali ho (ke doosron ko unki taraf mutawajjeh karey), lekin jab apney shohar ke paas ho to jaisi chahey khushbu laga ley."
4049,"Abul-Haseen Haisam bin Shafi ka bayan hai ke main aur mera eik sathi jiski kunniyat Abu-Aamir thi aur qabeela muaafir se talluq rakhta tha, ham rawana huey ke baitul-Maqdis mein ja kar Namaz padhi. un dino un logon ka waaize-qabeela azad ka eik aadmi tha jisey Abu Rihan kaha jata tha aur wo sahabi tha. Abul-Haseen ne kaha ke mera sathi mujh se pehley masjid mein chala gaya, main uskey baad pahuncha aur uskey sath ja baitha. usney mujh se puchha : kya tum ne Abu Rihan ki waaz (taqreer) se kuchh suna hai? maine kaha : nahin. usney kaha : maine usey kehtey huey suna hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne das baaton se mana farmaya hai :(1) daant bareek karwaaney se (un mein qadrey khula aa jaey aur khoobsurat nazar ayen). (2) jism gudwaaney se (ke us mein naqsh w nigaar banaey jaeyn ya naam waghaira likha jaey). (3) baal nauchne se (palkon aur chehrey ke, ki khoobsurat nazar aaye). (4) kisi mard ka kisi doosrey mard ke sath lipatney se jabkey unhoney kapdey na pehney huey hon. (5) kisi aurat ka dusri aurat ke sath lipatney se jabkey unhoney kapdey na pehney hon. (6) ajmiyon (ghair muslimon) ki tarah kapdon ke nichey reshmi astar laganey se. (7) ya ye ke koi ajmiyon ki tarah apney kandhon par reshmi chadar daley. (8) loot maar kerney se. (9) cheeton ki khaal bator guddi ya set istimal kerney se. aur (10) anguthi pehanney se siwaye iskey ke koi mansab daar ho. (to uskey liye jayez hai.) Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees mein anguthi ka zikr munfarid hai."
4050,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke surkh arghwani rang ke zeen poshon se mana kiya gaya hai.
4051,Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey mana farmaya ke soney ki anguthi pahnoon ya qassi (reshmi) libas ikhtiyar karun ya zeen posh surkh rang ka ho.
4052,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik munaqqash (chhapedar) ooni chadar mein Namaz padhi. aap ki nazar iskey nuqoosh par padi to jab Namaz se salam phera to farmaya : ''meri ye munaqqash chadar Abu-Jahm ke paas ley jao, usney mujhey abhi Namaz ke dauran mein mashghool kar diya tha merey liye saada (anbijaani) chadar ley aao . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Abu-Jahm bin Huzefa , bano Adi bin Kab bin Ghaanim ke fard they."
4053,"Usman bin Abi Sheba aur unke doosrey sathi bayan kartey hain ke Sufiyan ne Zohri ke wastey , Urwa sey, unhoney Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. aur mazkura baala riwayat ziyada Jaame hai."
4054,"Abdullah Abu-Umar se riwayat hai aur ye Sayeda Asma dukhtar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam they, unhoney bayan kiya ke maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko baazar mein dekha ke unhoney eik Shami kapda khareednaa chaha , phir dekha ke us mein surkh dhaagey padey hain to unhoney wapis kar diya. phir main Sayeda Asma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaya aur unhen ye waqia bataya to unhoney londi ko bulaya aur kaha : merey paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka jubba ley aao . to wo eik tailsaan ka ( mota ooni ( jubba ley aai jis ka daman , dono kaf aur dono taraf ke chaak motey reshmi dhaagey se kadhey huey they."
4055,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sirf usi kapdey se mana farmaya hai jo khalis reshmi ho. lekin agar reshmi dhaagey se kadhaai hui ho ya uska taanaa reshmi ho to us se koi harj nahin.
4056,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf aur Zuber bin Awam (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko resham ki qameesein pehanney ki ijazat di thi jabkey wo safar mein they aur unhen khaarish ho gaee thi.
4057,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne resham liya aur apney daain haath mein pakda aur sona liya aur apney baeyn haath mein pakda , phir farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye dono meri ummat ke mardon par haram hain.''"
4058,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Sayeda Umme-Kulsoom dukhtar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke unhoney Seeriya ki eik chadar audhi hui thi. yani dhaari daar reshmi chadar jis mein chaar khaney se baney huey they.
4059,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ladkon par se (resham) utaar liya kartey they aur bachchiyon par rehney detey they. Musaair kehtey hain ke maine is riwayat ke baarey mein Amr bin Dinar se puchha to unhoney la-ilmi ka izhar kiya.
4060,Janab Qatada kehtey hain ke ham ne Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kon sa libas sab se ziyada pasand tha? to unhoney kaha ke naqsh daar (ya dhaari daar .)
4061,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' safed kapdey pehna karo, bila-shuba ye tumharey kapdon mein sab se behtar hain aur unhi main apni maiyaton ko kafan diya karo . aur tumharey surmon mein sab se behtar surma Asmad hai jo nazar ko tez karta aur (palkon ke) baal ugata hai.''"
4062,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye . aapney eik aadmi ko dekha ke uskey baal bikhrey bikhrey se they. aapney farmaya : ''kya usey koi chiz nahin milti ke us se apney baalon ko sanwar ley?'' aur aapney eik-doosrey aadmi ko dekha jiskey kapdey meley ho rahey they. aapney farmaya : ''kya usey koi chiz nahin milti ke us se apney kapdey dho ley ?''
4063,"Janab abul-Ahwas ( Auf ( apney walid (Malik bin Nazla (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine ghatiya kapdey pehney huey they. aapney daryaft farmaya : ''kya tumharey paas maal hai? ''maine kaha : haan . aapney puchha kis qism ka ? maine arz kya ke Allah ne mujhey oont , bakriyan , ghodey aur ghulam her tarah ka maal inayat farmaya hua hai. aapney farmaya : ''jab Allah ne tumhen maal diya hai to uski nemat aur ehsan ka asar tujh par nazar aana chahiye .''"
4064,Janab Zaid bin Aslam bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) apni dadhi zard rang se ranga kartey they yahan tak ke unke kapdey bhi us rang se bhar jatey they. un se kaha gaya ke aap zard rang se kyon rangtey hain? unhoney kaha : yaqinan maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke wo usi se ( apney baal ya kapdey ( rangtey they aur unhen us se badh kar aur koi rang ziyada mehboob na tha aur wo apney sab kapdey usi se rangtey they yahan tak ke pagdi bhi .
4065,Hazrat abu-Ramsa (Rifa bin Yasribi) (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main apney walid ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan gaya to maine aap par sabz (hara) rang ki dhaari daar do chadaren dekhen.
4066,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada (Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se riwayat kartey hain ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik ghaati se nichey utrey. aap meri taraf mutawajjeh huey to dekha ke maine eik ikehri chadar li hui thi jo halkay asfari rang se rangi hui thi. aapney puchha : ''tum ne ye kaisi chadar apney ooper li hui hai? ''main aap ki na-pasandidgi ki wajeh samajh gaya. phir main apney ghar walon ke paas aaya aur wo apna tanur dehka rahey they to maine us chadar ko us mein dey maara. phir main agley din aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney daryaft farmaya : ''Abdullah ! us chadar ka kya hua ?'' maine aap ko batlaaya to aapney farmaya : ''tu ne usey apney ghar walon mein se kisi ko kyon na dey diya ? aurton ko to us mein koi harj nahin .''
4067,Hisham bin al-Ghaaz ne wazahat ki ke (المضرجة) se murad ye hai ke wo chadar na bahut surkh rang ki thi aur na gulaabi.
4068,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey dekha abu-Ali Lu Lu ke alfaz mein mera khayal hai ke mujh par kusum ke rang ka gulaabi kapda tha. aapney farmaya : ''ye kya hai? '' to main chala gaya aur usey jala dala, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''tum ne apney kapdey ka kya kya?'' maine kaha : maine usey jala dala hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : us riwayat ko Saur ne Khalid se riwayat kya to ( moorid ( kaha .) gulaabi se rang ki chadar thi. (aur Taaus ne ( معصفر ( kaha hai (kusum ke rang se rangi hui thi. ("
4069,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzra jis par surkh rang ke do kapdey they, usney aap ko salam kya magar aapney uskey salam ka jawab nahin diya."
4070,Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath rawana huey . aapney hamari sawaariyon aur oonton par zeen posh dekhey jin mein surkh rang ki oon ke dhaagey they. aapney farmaya : ''kya main nahin dekh raha ke ye surkh rang tum par ghalib aa raha hai? '' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us farman par ham is qadr jaldi se uthey ke us se hamarey kuch oont bhi bhag khadey huey aur ham ne apni wo chadaren un se utaar lein.
4071,"banu-Asad ki eik khatoon ka bayan hai ke main eik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja mohtarma ummul-momenin Sayeda Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan thi aur ham geru ke sath unke kapdey rang rahey they. ham ye kaam kar rahey they ke achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye . jab aapney geru dekha to lot gaey. Sayeda Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne ye baat dekhi to jaan gaeen ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye kaam pasand nahin aaya hai to unhoney kapdon ko dho dala aur sab surkhi ko chupa diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur andar jhaanka, pas jab aapney kuch na dekha to andar aagey ."
4072,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke baal aap ke kanon tak aatey they. aur maine aap ko dekha ke aap surkh rang ka joda pehney huey they. us se ziyada khoobsurat manzar maine kabhi nahin dekha .
4073,"Janab Hilal bin Aamir apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Mina mein dekha, jabke aap apney khachchar par se khutba dey rahey they aur aapney surkh rang ki dhaari daar chadar li hui thi. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke aagey they jo aap ki baat logon tak pahuncha rahey they."
4074,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye eik chadar ko siyah rang se rang diya, aapney usey pehna , magar jab us mein paseena aaya to aapney us mein oon ki bisaandh mehsoos ki to utaar phenka . raawi ne kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko umda khushbu hi pasand aati thi."
4075,Hazrat Jabir bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabkey aap ghutnon ko uthaey kapda lapetey bethey they aur shamley ( chadar ( ki kinaari aap ke qadmon par pad rahi thi.
4076,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Fateh Makka ke saal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) makkey mein dakhil huey to aap par siyah rang ki pagdi thi.
4077,"Janab Jaafar bin Amr bin Hurais apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko member par dekha, aap par siyah pagdi thi , uskey kinarey ko aapney apney kandhon ke darmiyan latkaaya hua tha."
4078,"abu-Jaafar bin Muhammad bin Ali bin Rukana apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rukana ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kashti ki thi to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko pachhaad diya tha. Rukana ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' hamarey aur mushrekin ke darmiyan topiyon par pagdiyan baandhney ka farq hai.''"
4079,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey pagdi baandhi aur uskey kinaron ko merey aagey ki taraf aur peechey ki janib latka diya.
4080,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do andaz se kapda lapetney se mana farmaya hai. eik ye ke aadmi kapda is tarah lapetey ke uski sharmgaah aasman ki janib khuli rahey. doosra yun ke kapda lapetey aur uska eik kinaara bahir nikal kar apney kandhey par dal ley .
4081,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne samma ke taur par kapda lapetney se mana kya hai. (yani insan puri tarah se us mein lipat jaey aur haath paon kuch bhi bahir na ho (aur eik kapdey ko apni kamar aur ghutnon par lapetney se bhi mana kya hai."
4082,"Janab Muawiya bin Qurra apney walid se bayan kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke main qabeela muzena ki jamaat ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua tha. ham ne aap ke sath baiat ki jabkey aap ki qamis ki ghundiyan khuli hui thin. kehtey hain ke ham ne bhi aap se baiat ki . phir maine apna haath aap ki qamis ke daman mein dal diya aur mohare-nabuwat ko chhua . Urwa kehtey hain ke baad Azan maine Muawiya aur unke sahibzadey ko jab bhi dekha sardi hoti ya garmi unki qameeson ki ghundiyaan khuli hoti thin aur wo unhen kabhi band na kartey they."
4083,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke) Makka ke dino ka zikr hai ke) aen do-pehar ke waqt ham apney ghar mein bethey huey they ke kisi ne Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ye sar aur chehra dhaanpey ( dhaata baandhey ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif la rahey hain aur aisey waqt mein aa rahey hain jo aap ka mamool nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye aur andar aaney ki ijazat chahi , aap ko ijazat di gaee to aap andar aagey ."
4084,"Hazrat Abu-Jari Jabir bin Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine eik shakhs ko dekha ke log uski baat khoob suntey aur mantey they. wo jo bhi kehta usey qubul kartey they. maine puchha ke ye kon hai? unhoney bataya ke ye Allah ke Rasool hain. . . (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) . . main bhi hazir ho gaya aur kaha ''aap par salamti ho aey Allah ke Rasool!'' maine ye do baar kaha . aapney farmaya : ye lafz ( عليك السلام ( mat kaho . ye maiyat ka tahiya aur salam hai. balke yun kaho : ( Assalamualaik ( ''maine kaha : ( kya (aap Allah ke Rasool hain? aapney farmaya : ''main us Allah ka bheja hua hun ke jab tumhen koi dukh pahunchey aur tum usey pukaro , to wo usey tum se door kar dey , agar tumhen khushk saali ka samna ho, tum us se dua karo to wo tumhari khetiyan uga dey . jab tum kisi sehra ya wiran aur banjar zameen mein ho aur tumhari sawari gum ho jaey aur tum usey pukaro to wo usey tumhen wapis lota dey .'' maine arz kya ke mujhey koi wasiyat farmaeyn . aapney farmaya : '' kisi ko gaali na dena .'' kehtey hain ke uskey baad maine kisi ko gaali nahin di kisi azad ko na ghulam ko , oont ko na bakri ko . aapney farmaya : '' kisi neki ko haqeer mat janna , apney bhai se baat karo to khuley chehrey se baat kya karo bila-shuba ye neki hai, aur apni chadar aadhi pindli tak oonchi rakha karo, aur agar na kar sako to takhnon tak kar saktey ho. ( takhnon se nichey ( chadar latkaaney se bachna . beshak ye takabbur hai aur Allah taala takabbur ko pasand nahin karta. aur agar koi shakhs tumhen bura bhala kahey aur tumhen tumhari kisi baat par jo wo janta ho aar dilaaey to tum uskey aeb par jo us mein ho usey aar mat dilaana, bila-shuba uska wabal usi par hoga.''"
4085,"Janab Salim bin Abdullah apney walid ( Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ne takabbur se apna kapda latkaayaa , Allah qiyamat ke roz uski taraf nahin dekhega .'' to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : merey tehband ka eik pallu dhila ho jata aur latak jata hai aur main uska khayal bhi bahut rakhta hun. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum un mein se nahin ho jo takabbur se aisa kartey hon.''"
4086,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke ittifaq se eik aadmi Namaz padh raha tha aur uska tehband takhnon se nichey latak raha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya : '' jao aur wuzu karo.'' chunanche wo gaya aur wuzu karkey aaya . phir aaya to aapney farmaya : '' jao aur wuzu karo.'' to eik aadmi ne aap se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya wajeh thi ke aapney usko wuzu kerney ka hukm diya phir aap khamosh ho rahey ? aapney farmaya : ''ye shakhs tehband latkaaey Namaz padh raha tha aur Allah taala ( takhney se nichey kapda ( latkaaney waley ( mard ( ki Namaz qubul nahin karta .''
4087,"Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen qism ke afrad se qiyamat ke roz Allah taala kalam nahin farmaeyga , na unki taraf dekhega , na unhen paak kerega aur unke liye dard naak azab hai.'' maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo kon hongey, bahut ghatey aur khasaray mein padey ye log ? aapney apni baat teen baar dohraai. maine arz kya : wo kon log hain, aey Allah ke Rasool ! wo bahut ghatey aur khasaray mein padey ? aapney farmaya : '' kapda latkaaney wala ( mard jo takhney se nichey kapda latkaaey ( ehsan karkey jatlaaney wala aur wo jo jhooti qasam se apna maal bechey .''"
4088,Hazrat abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye riwayat bayan ki . aur mazkura baala riwayat ziyada kamil hai. kaha ke) المنان ( se murad aisa aadmi hai jo jab bhi koi chiz dey to ehsan jatlaey .
4089,"Qais bin Bishr taghlabi ne kaha mujhey merey walid ne bayan kya, aur wo Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas betha kartey they. bayan kya ke dimashq mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Sahaba mein se eik sahab hotey they jinhen ibn Hanzala kaha jata tha. wo tanhai pasand aadmi they, logon ke sath bahut kam bethtey they. ya to Namaz padhtey hotey ya jab farigh ho jatey to tasbih w takbir mein mashghool rehtey aur phir apney ghar walon ke paas chaley jatey. wo hamarey paas se guzrey jabkey ham Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas bethey huey they. to abu-Darda ne un se kaha : koi eik baat bayan kar diijiye jis mein hamara faeyda ho jaey, us mein aap ka koi nuqsan nahin. unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik jamaat ko bheja . jab wo wapis aai to un mein se eik aadmi us majlis mein aa gaya jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif rakhtey they. to usney apney pehlu mein bethey huey aadmi se kaha : kash ke tum hamen dekhtey jab ham dushman se bhid gaey they aur falan ne neza maara aur kaha : lo ye mujh se aur main ghifaari jawan hun ! tumhari us baarey mein kya raey hai? sath waley ne kaha : main to samajhta hun ke uska ajr zaya ho gaya. ye baat doosrey ne suni to kaha : main to us mein koi harj nahin samajhta . un dono ki takraar honey lagi yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sun liya to farmaya : '' Subhanallah ! koi harj ki baat nahin ke usey ajr w sawab miley aur uski tareef bhi ho.'' to maine Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha ke us bayan se wo bahut khush huey . chunanche wo apna sar uthatey aur poochhtey they : kya bhala ye farman aapney khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha? to wo kehtey ke haan . aur ye baat unhoney un se baar baar puchhi. (us doran mein wo unke qarib bhi hotey ja rahey they ( yahan tak ke main samjha ke shayad ye unke ghutnon par beth jaeyngey . wo sahabi eik aur din hamarey paas se guzrey to Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : koi eik baat bayan kar diijiye jis mein hamara faeyda ho aur aap ka koi ghaata nahin hoga , to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen farmaya : '' ghodey par kharch kerney wala aisey hai jaisey usney apna haath sadqey mein khol rakha ho aur band na karta ho.'' wo sahabi eik aur din hamarey paas se guzrey to Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : koi kalma khair farma diijiye, us mein hamara faeyda hoga aur aap ka koi khasaara nahin, to unhoney bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Khurem Asadi behtareen aadmi hai agar uskey pattey ( sar ke baal ( lambey na hon aur apney tehband ko na latkaaey.'' ye baat Khurem ko pahunchi to unhoney jaldi se chhuri pakdi aur apney baalon ko kanon tak kaat liya aur apney tehband ko aadhi pindli tak ooncha kar liya . wo sahabi eik aur din hamarey paas se guzrey to Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne un se kaha : koi eik baat farmaeyn jo hamarey liye nafa mand ho aur us mein aap ka koi nuqsan nahin, to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''tum log apney bhaiyon ke paas pahunchney waley ho. chunanche apni sawaariyon ko durust kar lo , apney libas ki islah kar lo yahan tak ke aisey ho jao goya ke tum un mein se bahut numaya afrad ho. bila-shuba Allah taala be hayai ( ki baat ya kaam (aur jaan boojh kar aisa kerney ko pasand nahin farmata hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke abu-Nuem ne Hisham se riwayat kartey huey ye lafz yun kahey : ( حتى تكونوا كالشامة في الناس)"
4090,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bayan kya : ''Allah azz-w-jall farmata hai : badai meri ( ooper ki) chadar hai aur azmat meri ( nichey ki) chadar hai, chunanche jo koi in mein se kisi eik ko bhi khinchney ki koshish kerega ( mera shareek honey ki koshish kerega ( mein usey jahannam mein jhonk dunga .''"
4091,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiskey dil mein raai barabar bhi takabbur hua wo jannat mein dakhil nahin hoga aur jiskey dil mein raai barabar bhi emaan hua wo jahannam mein dakhil nahin hoga. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Qasamli ne Aamash se isi ki tarah riwayat kya hai.
4092,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur wo eik khoobsurat aadmi tha. usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey khoobsurti pasand hai aur mujhey ye hasil bhi hai jaisey ke aap dekh rahey hain, yahan tak ke main nahin chahta ke koi jootey ke tasmey mein bhi mujh se badh jaey. aur usney lafz ( بشراك نعلي ( kaha ya ( بشسع نعلي ( kya ye keyfiyat takabbur aur badai mein se hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, takabbur ye hai jo haq ko thukraaey aur logon ko haqeer janey .''"
4093,"Janab Ala bin Abdur-Rehman apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha ke maine Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se tehband ke mutalliq daryaft kya. to unhoney kaha ke sahibe-ilm w khabar se tumhara wasta pada hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' musalman ka tehband aadhi pindli tak hota hai. aadhi pindli se takhnon tak ke beech mein koi harj nahin aur jo takhnon se nichey ho wo aag mein hai, jisney takabbur se apna tehband ghasita Allah taala uski taraf nahin dekhega .''"
4094,"Janab Salim bin Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' isbaal '' yani ( had se ziyada ( kapda latkana tehband , qamis aur pagdi sabhi mein) mamnoo ( hai. jisney takabbur se un mein se kuch bhi latkaaya to qiyamat ke roz Allah taala uski taraf nazar nahin kerega .''"
4095,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kaha kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo kuch tehband ke baarey mein farmaya hai qamis ke baarey mein bhi uska yehi hukm hai.
4096,Janab Ikrima (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko tehband baandhey dekha ke unke tehband ka aglaa haashiya unke paon ki pusht ko chu raha hota aur peechey ki janib se ooper ko utha hota tha. maine kaha ke aap tehband us andaz se kyon baandhtey hain? unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko usi tarah baandhtey dekha hai.
4097,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat farmaai hai un aurton par jo mardon ki mushaabihat ikhtiyar keren aur un mardon par jo aurton ki mushaabihat ikhtiyar karen.
4098,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne lanat farmaai hai aisey mard par jo aurat jaisa libas pehney aur aisi aurat par jo mardon jaisa libas pehney.
4099,"Janab ibne-abi Mulaika se riwayat hai ke ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se kaha gaya ke) jo ( aurat ( mardon ke liye makhsus ( joota pahanti hai, ( uskey mutalliq aap ki kya raey hai? ( to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mardon ki tarah banney wali aurton par lanat farmaai hai."
4100,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne ansaar ki aurton ka zikr kya. unki tareef ki aur unke achey aamaal bayan kiye aur kaha : jab sura Noor nazil hui to un aurton ne pardon ke kapdey ya mardon ki chadaren lin . abu-Kaamil ko lafz ( حجور ) ya ( حجوز ( mein shak hua hai. . aur unhen phaad kar apney liye pardey ki chadaren bana liya .
4101,ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab aurton ke mutalliq ye hukm nazil hua ( يُدْنِينَ عَلَيْهِنَّ مِنْ . . .) '' wo apney ooper apni chadaren latka liya keren .'' to Ansari aurten jab bahir nikaltin to aisey lagta ke unke saron par koey bethey hon. un siyah chaadaron ki wajeh se jo wo apney saron par leney lagi thin.
4102,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Allah taala saabiq Muhajir khawatin par rehem farmaey. jab Allah ka ye hukm nazil hua ( وَلْيَضْرِبْنَ بِخُمُرِهِنَّ عَلَى جُيُوبِهِنَّ ( to unhoney oon ki moti-moti chadaren phaad kar apni odhniyaan bana lin. ibne-saleh ne ( أكنف (ke bajaey ( ) أكثف ( kaha hai.
4103,ibne-Shahab ne ye riwayat apni sanad se mazkura baala ke ham-maani riwayat ki hai.
4104,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke) unki behan ( Asma dukhtar Abu-Bakar Rasul Allah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ayen aur unhoney bareek kapdey pehney huey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se apna munh mod liya aur farmaya : ''aey Asma ! bachi jab jawan ho jaey to jayez nahin ke us se kuch nazar aaye siwaye iskey aur iskey aur aapney apney chehrey aur haathon ki taraf ishara farmaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye riwayat mursal hai. Khalid bin Duraik ne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko nahin paya . aur Saeed bin Bashir qawi nahin hai.
4105,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se seengi lagwaaney ki ijazat chahi . to aapney abu-Taiba ko farmaya ke usey seengi lagaey . raawi ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke wo unka doodh shareek bhai tha ya naabaaligh ladka tha.
4106,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke liye eik ghulam laye jo aapney unko hiba kya tha. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) par aisa kapda tha ke wo agar usey sar par lapet-tin to unke paon tak na pahunchta tha, aur agar paon ko chhipaatin to sar par na rehta tha. pas jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski us uljhan ko dekha to farmaya : ''tumharey liye koi harj ki baat nahin, tumharey samney sirf tumharey walid hain aur tumhara ghulam .''"
4107,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke eik hijda Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaj ke gharon mein aata jata tha aur log uskey baarey mein samajhtey they ke us mein aurton ki taraf koi mailan nahin aur ye (غير أولي الإربة) mein se hai. eik din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye aur wo aap ki kisi biwi ke paas betha hua tha aur eik aurat ki tareef mein yun keh raha tha ke wo jab samney se aati hai to uskey pet par chaar bal padtey hain aur jab kamar pher kar jati hai to aath se wapis hoti hai (yani pahluon ki taraf se chaar chaar bal nazar aatey hain jo uskey moti-tazi aur khoobsurat honey ki alamat hain ( to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main nahin samajhta tha ke ye bhi in aurton ki makhfii baaten janta hai, aainda ye tumharey yahan hergiz na aaya karey.'' chunanche usey rok diya gaya."
4108,Zohri ne Urwa se unhoney Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se is hadees ke ham-maani riwayat ki hai.
4109,"ibne-Shahab ( Zohri ( Urwa sey, unhoney Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se ye hadees riwayat ki . us mein mazeed ye hai ke aur usey ( Madina tayiba sey) nikal diya. chunanche wo maqame-Beda mein rehta tha aur her Juma aata aur khaney peeney ki chizen mang kar ley jaya karta tha."
4110,"Janab Auzaai ne is qissey mein bayan kya ke kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ( agar usey gharon se rok diya gaya to ( ye bhook se mar jaeyga . to aapney usey ijazat di ke her haftey do baar aa jaya karey, logon se sawal karey aur lot jaya karey."
4111,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne aayat kareema (وَقُلْ لِلْمُؤْمِنَاتِ يَغْضُضْنَ مِنْ أَبْصَارِهِنَّ) ki tafseer mein farmaya : (ye aam hukm tha. phir badi umr ki boodhi aurton ke haq mein) isey mansookh karkey unhen is hukm se mustashnaa kartey huey farmaya : ( وَالْقَوَاعِدُ مِنْ النِّسَاءِ . . . الخ ( yani badi umr ki boodhi aurten jinhen ab nikah ki khahish na ho. . .(un par pardey ke ehkam ki pabandi nahin hai.)
4112,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein mojud thi jabkey Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) bhi wahin thin ke Hazrat ibne Umme-Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) aa-gey. aur ye un dino ki baat hai jabkey hamein pardey ke ehkam dey diye gaey they. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is se parda karo. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hukm azwaaje-Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (aapki biwiyon) ke liye khas tha. jabkey Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anha) ko ibne Umme- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan iddat guzaarney ka kaha gaya tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey farmaya tha : ''ibne Umme- Maktum ke yahan iddat guzaaro , wo na-bina aadmi hai, tum uskey yahaan apney kapdey utaar sako-gi.''"
4113,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi apney ghulam ki apni baandi se shaadi kar dey to ab us baandi ke sattar ki taraf na dekhay.''
4114,Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se jab koi apni khaadima ki apney ghulam ya naukar se shaadi kar dey to ab us khaadima ki naaf se lekar ghutney se ooper tak ke hissey ko mat dekhey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke sanad mein raawi (Dawud bin Sawwaar) ka sahih naam sawar bin Dawud Muzni Sairfi hai. is mein Wakee ko weham hua hai.
4115,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) iskey yahaan aaye aur wo sar par audhni lapet rahi thin . to aapney farmaya : ''eik bal do, do (2) nahin. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : iska mafhoom ye hai ke audhni ko is tarah mat lapetey ke mardon ki pagdi mehsoos ho. kapdey ko do bal mat dey."
4116,"Hazrat Dahiya bin khalifa Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas Misr ke safed bareek kapdey laye gaey to aapney un mein se eik kapda mujhey bhi inayat farmaya aur kaha : ''iskey do tukdey kar lo, eik ki tum qamis bana lo aur doosra apni ehliya ko dey do, wo isko apni audhni bana ley.'' phir jab maine pusht pheri to aapney farmaya : ''apni biwi ko kehna ke iskey nichey koi aur kapda laga ley ke uskey jism ko zahir na karey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is hadees ko Yahya bin Ayub ne riwayat kiya to (Musa bin Jubair ke ustaad ka naam) Abbas bin Ubaidullah bin Abbas bayan kiya."
4117,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab tehband ka zikr kiya to Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne aurat ke mutalliq puchha ke wo isey kis qadr lamba karey? aapney farmaya : ''eik baalisht latka ley.'' Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : is se to uskey paon nangey hongey . aapney farmaya : ''eik haath latka ley aur is se ziyada na karey.''
4118,"Naafe ne Sulaiman bin Yasar sey, unhoney Sayeda Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees bayan ki hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke ye riwayat ibne Is-haq aur Ayub bin Musa ne ba-waasta Naafe Sayeda Safiya (Raziallahu anha) se bayan ki hai."
4119,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Ummahaatul-momineen ko ijazat di ke apni chaadaron ke pallu eik baalisht lambey rakha karen. phir unhoney mazeed lambey kerney ki ijazat chahi to aapney eik aur baalisht badhaney ka farmaya. chunanche wo hamein iske liye kahtin to ham unke liye un chaadaron ke pallu eik-eik haath lambey rakhtey.
4120,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke hamari eik baandi ko sadqe ki eik bakri hadiya ki gaee phir wo mar gaee. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''tum ne iskey chamdey ko rang kyon nahin liya, is se koi fayda utha letey?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye murdar hai. aapney farmaya : ''haram to iska khana hai.''"
4121,"Maamer ne Zohri ke wastey bayan kiya, (lekin) Zohri ki is hadees ki sanad mein Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr nahin hai. is mein hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne iskey chamdey se fayda kyon nahin uthaya?'' aur is mein rangney ka zikr nahin kiya."
4122,"Maamer kehtey hain ke Janab (ibne-Shahab) Zohri (Rahimahullah) (halal janwar ke chamdey ko) rangney ka inkar kartey they. unka kehna tha ke her haal mein fayda uthana jayez hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Zohri ki is riwayat mein Auzaai , Yunus aur Aqeel ne rangney ka zikr nahin kiya. jabkey Zubaidi ne uska zikr kiya hai. aisey hi Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez aur Hafs bin Waleed ne bhi rangney ka zikr kiya hai."
4123,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : '' chamdey ko jab rang liya jaey to wo paak ho jata hai.''"
4124,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya ke murdar ke chamdey se faeyda uthaya jaey. . . (yani ( jab usey rang liya jaey.
4125,Hazrat Salma bin Mohbiq (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ghazwae-tabuk ke moqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ghar mein aaye to eik mishkeeza latkey dekha. to aapney pani talab farmaya : to unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye mishkeeza murdar (janwer ke chamdey ka ( hai. aapney farmaya : ''isko rang diya jana iski pakizgi hai.''
4126,"Aaliya dukhtar Sabee'a bayan karti hain ke uhud ki janib meri bakriyan hoti thin. hua ye ke wo marna shuru ho gaeen to main Ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aai aur un se iska zikr kiya. Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne mujh se kaha : agar tum unke chamdey utaar liya karo to un se fayda uthaogi. kehti hain ke maine puchha : kya ye halal hain? unhoney kaha : haan. Quraish ke kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se guzrey , wo eik bakri ghasitey ja rahey they jaisey ke gadhaa ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : ''tum iska chamdaa hi utaar letey.'' unhoney kaha : ye murdar hai. aapney farmaya : ''isey pani aur qaraz paak kar deta hai.'' (qaraz keekar ki manind eik darkht hota hai jo chamdaa saaf karney mein istimal hota hai.)"
4127,Janab Abdullah bin Akeem se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : qabeela juhaina ke ilaqey mein hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik khat padh kar sunaya gaya jabkey main nau-umr jawan ladka tha : ''ye ke murdar ke chamdey ya uskey putthon se fayda mat uthao.''
4128,"Hakam bin utaibaa kehtey hain ke main aur kaee log Abdullah bin Akeem ke yahan gaey, wo qabeela juhaina ke fard they. Hakam ne kaha : doosrey log andar chaley gaey jabke main darwazey par baitha raha. chunanche jab wo merey paas wapis aaye to unhoney mujhey bataya ke Abdullah bin Akeem ne unhen bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni wafat se eik mahina pehley qabeela juhaina ki taraf eik khat likha tha : ''murdar ke chamdey ya uskey putthon se fayda mat uthao. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Nazar bin Shumeil ne kaha ke be rangey chamdey ko (إهاب) kehtey hain. rang diye janey ke baad usey (إهاب) nahin kehtey balke (شن) aur (قربة) kehtey hain."
4129,"Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''khaz (resham) ke kapdey aur chheetey ki khaal ko apni gaddi mat banao.'' (inhen bataur zeen ya zeen posh istimal na karo.) ibne Sirin ne kaha : Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat hadees mein muttahim (jis par jhoot waghaira ka ilzam laga ho) nahin they. (unki siyaasi aaraa se kisi ko ikhtilaf ho to alag baat hai warna farmaane-Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki naqal mein nihayat qabile-aitimad (bharose ke qabil) they. ("
4130,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis jamaat mein chheetey ki khaal ho uskey sath (rehmat ke) farishtey nahin chaltey.''
4131,"Janab Khalid bin Maadaan se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb, Amr bin Aswad aur qabeela banu-Asad ka eik aadmi jo ehale Qinnsireen mein se tha, Hazrat Muawiya bin Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaye. Muawiya ne Miqdam se kaha : kya tumhen maloom hai ke Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) wafat pa gaey hain? to Miqdam ne (انا لله وانا اليه راجعون) padha. to eik aadmi ne un se kaha : kya tum isko musibat samajhtey ho? unhoney kaha : main unki wafat ko musibat kyon na samjhoon jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko apni god mein bithaya tha aur kaha tha : ''ye (Hasan) mujh se hai aur Husain Ali se ! ''Asadi aadmi ne kaha : dehakta koila tha jisey Shan Wale Allah ne bujha diya. Miqdam ne kaha : magar (main to aisi baat nahin kehta jo is Asadi ne kahi hai) main aaj tumhen ghussa dila ke rahunga aur wo kuchh sunaunga jo tumhen bura lagey. phir kaha : aey Muawiya ! agar main sach kahun to meri tasdeeq karna aur agar ghalat kahun to tardeed (radd) kar dena. Muawiya ne kaha : aisey hi karunga . Miqdam ne kaha : main tumhen Allah ki qasam de-kar kehta hun kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sona pehanney se mana farmaya hai? kaha haan. Miqdam ne phir kaha : main tumhen Allah ki qasam de-kar kehta hun kya tumhen khabar hai ke, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne resham pehanney se roka hai? unhoney kaha : haan. Hazrat Miqdam ne kaha : main tumhen Allah ki qasam de-kar kehta hun, kya tum jantey ho ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darindon ki khalen pehanney aur un-par Sawar honey se roka hai? kaha : haan. Miqdam ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! maine ye sab kuchh tumharey ghar mein dekha hai aey Muawiya ! is par Muawiya ne kaha : aey Miqdam ! mujhey maloom tha ke main tujh se hergiz nahin bach sakoon ga. Khalid bin Maadaan ne bayan kiya ke phir Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Miqdam ke liye is qadr inaam ka hukm diya jo uskey doosrey do sathiyon ke liye nahin tha aur unke bete ke liye do-sau walon mein hissey muqarrar kar diya. chunanche Hazrat Miqdam (Raziallahu anhu) ne isey apney sathiyon mein taqseem kar diya. magar Asadi ne jo wasul kiya us mein se kisi ko kuchh na diya. Muawiya ko ye khabar pahunchi to unhoney kaha : Miqdam khulay haath ke sakhi aadmi hain aur Asadi apney maal ki khoob hifazat kerney wala hai."
4132,Janab Abu-Maleeh bin Usama apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne darindon ki khalen istimal karney se mana farmaya hai.
4133,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhoney kaha : ham eik safar mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they. aapney farmaya : ''jootey khoob pehna karo, bila-shuba aadmi jab tak joota pehney ho to (goya) wo Sawaar hota hai.''"
4134,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke jootey mein do pattiyaan hoti thin .
4135,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke aadmi khadey ho kar joota pehney .
4136,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi shakhs eik jootey mein na chaley , chahiye ke dono pehney ya dono utaar dey .''"
4137,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ke jootey ka tasma toot jaey to jab tak usey durust na kar ley eik jootey mein na chaley , na eik mozey mein chaley aur na baaein hath se khaye .''"
4138,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : sunnat ye hai ke aadmi jab bethey to apney jootey utaar ley aur apney pehlu mein rakh ley ."
4139,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi joota pehney to daain ( taraf ( se ibtida (shuruat) karey aur jab utarey to baain se shuru karey, daayan paon pehanney mein pehley aur utaarney mein aakhiri hona chahiye .''"
4140,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney tamam kamon mein jahan tak ho sakta daain janib ko pasand farmatey they. wuzu kerney , kanghi kerney aur joota pehanney mein . Muslim bin Ibrahim ne miswak ka bayan bhi kya magar ( في شأنه كله ( '' tamam kamon '' ka zikr nahin kya.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Muaz ne Shoba se riwayat kya to us mein miswak ka zikr nahin kya."
4141,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum libas pahno ya wuzu karo to apni daain janib se shuru kya karo.''
4142,"Saiyedna Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bistaron ka zikr kya, to farmaya : '' eik bistar aadmi ka , doosra biwi ka aur teesra mehman ka hai aur chotha shetan ke liye hai.''"
4143,Hazrat Jabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar gaya to maine aap ko dekha ke aap eik takiye ka sahara liye huey they. Abdullah bin Jarrah ne kaha : aap apney baain pehlu se sahara liye huey they. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : is riwayat ko Is-haq bin Mansoor ne bhi Israel se riwayat kaha ( to kaha ke) aap baaein pehlu se sahara liye huey they.
4144,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Yamen se aaye huey kuch rufaqaaye safar ko dekha jin ki sawariyon ke paalan chamdey ke they, to unhoney kaha : jo shakhs chahta hai ke aisey logon ko dekhay jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rufaqaaye safar ke bahut ziyada mushabeh hon to wo unhen dekh ley ."
4145,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : ''kya tumharey haashiye daar bistar ya unki chadaren hain?'' maine arz kya : hamarey liye chaadarein ya bistar kahan ? aapney farmaya : '' an-qareeb tum khoobsurat nafis haashiya daar bistar ya chadaren hasil karogey .''"
4146,"ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik takiya tha. ibne-Munee ne kaha . . . takiya chamdey ka tha jis par aap raat ko sotay they, phir riwayat ke agley alfaz bayan kerney mein dono raawi muttafiq hain. . . us mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi."
4147,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka gaddaa chamdey ka tha jis mein khajoor ki chhaal bhari hui thi.
4148,ummul-momenin Sayeda umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke mera bichona Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaey Namaz ke samney hota tha.
4149,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif ley gaey, unke darwazey par parda dekha to aap andar dakhil na huey . Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : bahut kam aisey hota ke aap ghar jaeyn (aur unke yahan na jaeyn (aur phir unke yahan se ibtida (shuruat) kartey. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aaye to Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko dekha ke ghamgin hain. puchha ke tumhen kya hua hai? unhoney kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan aaye they magar andar dakhil nahin huey . chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Fatima ko ye baat badi giraan guzri hai ke aap uskey yahan gaey magar andar dakhil nahin huey . aapney farmaya : ''main kya aur duniya kya? ( mujhey duniya se kya sarokaar ? ( mein kya aur naqsh daar pardey kya ?'' ( mera un se kya wasta) chunanche wo Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaey aur usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat batlaai. pas unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se poochen ke merey liye kya hukm hai? aapney farmaya : ''usey kaho ke usey bani falan ke paas bhej dey .''"
4150,ibn Fuzel ne apney walid se ye hadees bayan ki to kaha : parda naqsh daar tha.
4151,ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghar mein koi bhi chiz dekhtey jis par saleeb ka nishan hota to usey kaat daltey they.
4152,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis ghar mein tasweer ya kutta ya junbi ho, us mein farishtey dakhil nahin hotey .''"
4153,"Hazrat abu-Talha Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey suna : ''jis ghar mein kutta ho ya but wahan farishtey dakhil nahin hotey .'' Zaid bin Khalid ne abu-Talha se kaha : chalo ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se is baarey mein poochhtey hain. chunanche ham chal diye . ham ne kaha : aey ummul-momenin ! abu-Talha hamen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yun yun bayan kartey hain. kya aapney bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye bayan kartey suna hai? unhoney kaha : nahin. lekin main tumhen wo batati hun jo maine unhen kartey huey dekha hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney eik safar mein tashrif ley gaey . mujhey aap ki wapsi ka intizar tha. maine apna eik haashiya daar parda liya aur usey shehteer ke sath latka diya. jab aap tashrif laye to maine istiqbal kya aur arz kya : السلام عليك ya رسول الله ورحمة الله وبركاته hamd us Allah ki jisney aap ko izzat aur ikram se nawaza hai. aapney ghar par nazar dali to wo haashiya daar parda dekha aur mujhey koi jawab na diya. mujhey aap ke chehrey par nagawari mehsoos hui . phir aap us haashiya daar pardey ki taraf aaye aur usey utaar phenka , phir farmaya : '' beshak Allah ne hamen hamarey rizq mein ye hukm nahin diya ke inton aur patharon ko kapdey pehnatey phiren .'' kehti hain chunanche maine usko phaad kar do takiye bana liye aur un mein khajoor ki chhaal bhar di. to us par aapney mujhey kuch nahin kaha ."
4154,Jarir ne Suhel se apni sanad se usi mazkura hadees ki misl riwayat kya. us mein hai ke Zaid bin Khalid ne kaha : meri ammaan jaan ! us ( abu-Talha Ansari ( ne mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye hadees bayan ki hai. us riwayat ki sanad mein Saeed bin Yasar ke mutalliq hai ke ye bano najaar ke ghulam they.
4155,"Hazrat abu-Talha ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba farishtey us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jis mein tasweer ho.'' Janab Basar bin Saeed ne kaha : phir aisey hua ke (us hadees ke raawi yani hamarey Shekh ( Zaid bin Khalid bimar ho gaey aur ham unki iyaadat ko gaey to dekha ke unke darwazey par parda hai aur us mein tasweer thi. maine Ubaidullah Kholani se kaha, jo ke ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke parwarda they, bhala Zaid ne guzishta din tasweeron ke mutalliq hadees bayan nahin ki thi ? to Ubaidullah ne kaha : to kya tum ne suna nahin tha jabkey unhoney kaha tha : siwaey iske ke kisi kapdey par koi naqsh w nigaar ho."
4156,Saiyedna Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Fateh Makka ke moqe par hukm diya jabkey aap khud wadi Bat'ha mein thehrey huey they ke Kaaba mein jaeyn aur us mein mojud sab tasweeron ko mita dalen . chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) un tasweeron ke mita diye janey tak us mein dakhil nahin huey they.
4157,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tehqiq Jibrael Alehissalam ne aaj raat mujh se mulaqat ka wada kiya tha, magar mulaqat ko na aaye.'' mujhey khayal aaya ke hamari chaarpai ke nichey kuttey ka pilla mojud hai (kahin ye hi maane (rukawat) na hua ho) to uskey nikalney ka hukm diya. phir aapney pani liya aur apney haath se us jagah chhidak diya. phir Jibrael Alehissalam se mulaqat hui to unhoney kaha : '' beshak ham us ghar mein dakhil nahin hotey jahan kutta ho ya tasweer ho.'' phir subah hui to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kutton ko maarney ka hukm diya, yahan tak ke aap chhotey baaghon ke kutton ko bhi maarney ka hukm detey they, albatta badey baaghon ke kutton ko chhod detey they."
4158,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Jibrael Alehissalam merey paas aaye aur mujhey kaha : main guzishta raat aap ke yahan aaya tha magar andar aaney se merey liye ye Amr maane (baat rukawat) tha ke (aap ke ghar ke) darwazey par taswiren thin aur ghar mein tasweeron wala parda tha aur kutta bhi tha, chunanche aap ghar mein tasweer ke mutalliq hukm dijiye ke uska sar kaat diya jaey aur darkht ki manind ho jaey aur pardey ke mutalliq hukm farmaeyn ke usey kaat kar do takiye bana liye jaeyn jo phenkey jaeyn aur paon se raundey jaeyn aur kuttey ke mutalliq farmaiye ke usey nikal bahir kiya jaey.'' chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aisey hi kiya. ye kutta Hasan ya Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka tha jo unke takht ke nichey tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya aur usey nikal bahir kiya gaya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke (النضد) se murad wo cheez hai jis par kapdey rakhey jatey hain aur wo chaarpai ke mushabeh (jaisi) hoti hai."
